<item>
            <title>[HBASE-4418] Show all the hbase configuration in the web ui</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4418</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The motivation is to show ALL the HBase configuration, which takes effect in the run time, in a global place.&lt;br/&gt;
So we can easily know which configuration takes effect and what the value is.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The configuration shows all the HBase and DFS configuration entry in the configuration file and also includes all the HBase default setting in the code, which is not the config file.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
